<title>FRANCE: Alcatel breakdown of operating income.</title>
<headline>Alcatel breakdown of operating income.</headline>
<dateline>PARIS 1997-03-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Alcatel Alsthom gave the following breakdown of its operating income in billions of francs.</p>
<p>				  1996		    1995</p>
<p>    Operating income	 2.9	vs	   0.6</p>
<p>    - telecoms     loss    0.8	vs   loss  3.3</p>
<p>    - cables		   2.1	vs	   2.3</p>
<p>    - 50 pct GEC Alsthom   1.4	vs	   1.3</p>
<p>    - systems	loss    0.1	vs   loss  0.4</p>
<p>    - batteries		0.3	vs	   0.2</p>
<p>    - others		   0.0	vs	   0.5</p>
<p>    Financial loss	   0.7	vs	   1.5</p>
<p>    restructuring costs    0.5	vs	  13.4</p>
<p>    write down of goodwill 2.2	vs	  13.5</p>
<p>    pre-tax		    2.7	vs  loss  26.0</p>
<p>    tax charge		 0.7	vs	   1.2</p>
<p>    net financial debt    13.1	vs	  20.0</p>
<p>    shareholders funds    40.8	vs	  33.0</p>
<p>    provisions		51.0	vs	  50.6</p>
<p>    gearing (pct)	   32	  vs	  61</p>
<p>NOTE -- Alcatel gave the figures during a news conference.</p>
</text>
